Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼宮春日的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:16.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}翻譯：spirit ZERO；校對：NT000A；後期：zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…咳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是情人節呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為以參加一切活動為宗旨的SOS團來說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已給你們準備了巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為我們SOS團就這麼把巧克力給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後說「好！結束」可就太沒趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  男生也不能白拿  必須…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出點努力！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要咱倆做啥！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太隨性啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說為了讓你們願意送出巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須做出點行動才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我就是這意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別這麼就贊同啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:56.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（走廊）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  你有什麼提議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:00:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  倒不是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發訊息讓人準備必要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也不是不能讓「做點什麼」這件事本身都化有為無
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如  這裡有巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個…情人節快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾  贈送失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我就由索取者變為了贈送者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說別人必須為我「做點什麼」了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…即使這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從春日她們那得到東西的前提沒變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己還是得「做點什麼」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你看穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  只是消磨點時間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  請你稍微退後點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是路過的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  都齊全了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連新川先生都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼咱們換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？換成啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥換西裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們現在身份是男公關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男公關？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到對女性「做點什麼」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想到男公關了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看起來像男公關嗎  森小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  外表是沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差微笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說「男公關就是用微笑殺死女性」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森小姐  你這是殺氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  也沒別的辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅惑的普通人  虛雲！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣是初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深紅的超級球  射月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  笨蛋阿虛  都把實玖瑠弄哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別弄那奇怪的打扮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（生氣了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（同時）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這壓迫感…是什麼人？

